            "name": "base-build",
            "hidden": true,
            "description": "Capped at 4 parallel jobs rather than 0 (== one job per core). Several TUs here are memory-hungry, and an unbounded job count on a high-core CPU can exceed system RAM, thrash the pagefile and orphan cc1plus/as.exe when a job OOMs. Override per-invocation with '--parallel N'.",
            "jobs": 4
        },
